PWA - HTTPS
-----
Prevents bad actors from tampering with communication between app and browser.
Encrypts data.

Why needed in Progressive Web Apps?
They use some features which require HTTPS for security reasons.
Although it's needed for PWA, should always be using HTTPS anyway.

letsencrypt.org, a free automated and open certificate authority.
Cloudflare is a CDN. Can use as your personal server and automatically get HTTPS.